items.title: Yarrow algorithm - Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
items.snippet:
The Yarrow algorithm is a family of cryptographic pseudorandom number 
generator (PRNG) devised by John Kelsey, Bruce Schneier and Niels Ferguson.
